# PwC Power BI Virtual Case Experience (Forage)

This repository showcases my work completed during the **PwC Power BI Virtual Internship** offered by [Forage](https://www.theforage.com/). 
The internship simulated real-world data analytics tasks and involved creating interactive dashboards to generate business insights using Power BI.

## ðŸ“Š Tasks Completed

### 1. Call Center Trends Analysis
- Analyzed support ticket volume and resolution trends.
- Visualized performance by ticket type and department.
- Created KPIs to monitor agent workload and response time.

### 2. Customer Retention Dashboard
- Built a churn analysis dashboard using customer data.
- Identified key churn drivers: contract type, payment method, and service usage.
- Developed KPIs such as Churn Rate, Customer Lifetime Value, and Revenue Loss.
- Suggested data-driven strategies to improve retention.

### 3. Diversity & Inclusion Insights
- Evaluated organizational diversity using gender and department data.
- Visualized representation across different business units.
- Proposed strategies to improve diversity balance and inclusive hiring.

